'She's controversial, but so was Marilyn Monroe': Kim Kardashian gets the ultimate compliment from former French Vogue editor Carine Roitfeld
By
Tamara Abraham
PUBLISHED:
11:00 EST, 22 October 2013
| UPDATED:
